comments: Professor Scott is a real Southern sweetheart. She is especially caring, nice and makes class easygoing/relaxed. The class is not very demanding, it\'s how a core curriculum class should be! Even two years after her class, she still recognizes me on campus and is always friendly and smiles. Calls her students "darling" and "angel" like a grandma.
